The engine source files are located in the parent data folder of the engine-script.dll specified in the .csproj file.
You can use any public function and class defined there.
Try to use and find the provided utilities from the engine like math, random, physics etc.
Enitiy is a struct and cannot be compared to null. Either use IsValid() or castable to bool operator. if(entity) or if(!entity)

Do not create or modify real assets like prefabs and meta files.

When writing or modifyign rcss files do not use soild keyword.
Only use RmlUi supported properties described in https://mikke89.github.io/RmlUiDoc/pages/rcss/property_index.html and https://mikke89.github.io/RmlUiDoc/pages/rcss/font_effects.html and https://mikke89.github.io/RmlUiDoc/pages/rcss/filters.html

Ahe alpha value of colors in rcss is not 0-1 but 0-255